ABOUT
------
Fortuner shows a fortune as a notification. Requires the fortune
program, libnotify and GTK+ 2.

INSTALLATION
-------------
1) Install the requirements
   An example for Debian GNU/Linux:
   # apt-get install libgtk2.0-dev cmake fortune-mod libnotify-dev

2) Clone the repository (get sources)
   $ git clone git://github.com/jnumm/fortuner.git

3) Build the program
   $ cd fortuner
   $ cmake .
   $ make

3) Now you can run Fortuner:
   $ cd bin
   $ ./fortuner

BUGS
-----
Please report bugs to https://github.com/jnumm/fortuner/issues.

